{"type":"message","id":"cf579126","parentId":"e96604bb","timestamp":"2026-03-09T18:25:49.947Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Tue 2026-03-10 02:25 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 批量发布所有35个Skills到ClawHub（使用正确端点）\n\nAPI信息：\n- 端点: https://clawhub.ai/api/v1\n- Token: clh_1fCyGAxj2bNgAqc3UmhZZJ9z4F0dbHAAVFlyzIEOPaA\n\n需要发布的35个Skills（现在本地都有文件了）：\n1. config-format-converter (免费版带Gumroad钩子)\n2. batch-file-renamer (免费版带Gumroad钩子)\n3. qr-code-tool (免费版带Gumroad钩子)\n4. rest-api-tester (免费版带Gumroad钩子)\n5. ssl-certificate-checker\n6. http-headers-analyzer\n7. cron-expression-parser\n8. docker-compose-validator\n9. json-path-query\n10-35. 其他26个Skills\n\nAPI调用格式：\n```bash\ncurl -X POST \"https://clawhub.ai/api/v1/skills\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer clh_1fCyGAxj2bNgAqc3UmhZZJ9z4F0dbHAAVFlyzIEOPaA\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"name\": \"skill-name\",\n    \"content\": \"<base64-encoded-content>\",\n    \"source\": \"github\",\n    \"visibility\": \"public\"\n  }'\n```\n\n如果API返回401，可能需要不同的认证方式（检查文档）\n如果API返回403，Token权限不足\n如果API返回409，Skill已存在（更新即可）\n\n发布完成后：\n1. 记录每个Skill的发布状态（成功/失败/已存在）\n2. 更新skill-registry.json的publishStatus和clawhubUrl\n3. 汇报成功发布的Skills列表和URL"}],"timestamp":1773080749931}}
{"type":"message","id":"214d1938","parentId":"cf579126","timestamp":"2026-03-09T18:25:53.731Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to batch publish 35 Skills to ClawHub. Let me break down what I need to do:\n\n1. First, I need to find all the skills in the workspace\n2. Read the skill-registry.json to understand the current state\n3. Publish each skill to ClawHub using the API\n4. Update the registry with publish status and URLs\n\nLet me start by exploring the workspace to find all skills and the registry file.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"read:0","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/memory/skill-registry.json"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /workspace/projects/workspace/skills/","workdir":"/workspace/projects/workspace"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"kimi-k2-5-260127","usage":{"input":8014,"output":148,"cacheRead":3328,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":11490,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773080749946}}
