{"type":"message","id":"5cbe6e77","parentId":"acbc0617","timestamp":"2026-03-09T18:33:20.241Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I've completed the analysis. Let me provide a comprehensive summary to the main agent about what was attempted, what was discovered, and what needs to be done next.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## Summary Report: ClawHub Batch Publish Attempt\n\n### Attempt Status\n**BLOCKED** - API authentication works but missing file storage infrastructure.\n\n### What Was Attempted\n- **32 Skills** prepared for publishing\n- **API Endpoint**: `https://clawhub.ai/api/v1/skills`\n- **Authentication**: Token is valid (GET requests work)\n\n### Technical Findings\n\n#### API Works For:\n✅ Authentication  \n✅ Listing skills (GET /api/v1/skills)  \n✅ Getting skill details (GET /api/v1/skills/{slug})  \n\n#### API Blocked For:\n❌ Publishing new skills - requires `storageId` for files\n\n#### Required Payload Structure (Discovered):\n```json\n{\n  \"slug\": \"skill-name\",\n  \"displayName\": \"Skill Name\",\n  \"version\": \"1.0.0\", \n  \"changelog\": \"Initial release\",\n  \"visibility\": \"public\",\n  \"summary\": \"Description\",\n  \"source\": {\n    \"type\": \"github\",\n    \"url\": \"...\",\n    \"owner\": \"...\",\n    \"repo\": \"...\",\n    \"path\": \"...\",\n    \"commit\": \"main\",\n    \"kind\": \"github\",\n    \"ref\": \"refs/heads/main\",\n    \"importedAt\": 1234567890000\n  },\n  \"files\": [{\n    \"path\": \"SKILL.md\",\n    \"name\": \"SKILL.md\", \n    \"content\": \"base64...\",\n    \"size\": 1234,\n    \"sha256\": \"...\",\n    \"storageId\": \"REQUIRED_FROM_UPLOAD\",\n    \"encoding\": \"base64\"\n  }]\n}\n```\n\n### Missing Infrastructure\nThe API requires a `storageId` that must be obtained by uploading files first. These endpoints were tested but all returned 404:\n- POST /api/v1/files\n- POST /api/v1/storage/upload  \n- POST /api/v1/blobs\n- POST /api/v1/skills/upload\n\n### Skills Ready to Publish (32 Total)\nAll files are prepared at `/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/*/SKILL.md` and synced to GitHub:\n1. config-format-converter\n2. batch-file-renamer\n3. qr-code-tool\n4. rest-api-tester\n5. ssl-certificate-checker\n6. http-headers-analyzer\n7. cron-expression-parser\n8. docker-compose-validator\n9. json-path-query\n10. password-generator\n11. csv-processor\n12. markdown-formatter\n13. system-health-check\n14. url-encoder\n15. csv-data-analyzer\n16. text-diff-comparator\n17. json-schema-validator\n18. url-shortener-expander\n19. regex-tester\n20. color-code-converter\n21. base64-toolkit\n22. jwt-token-inspector\n23. sql-formatter\n24. meeting-summarizer\n25. data-format-converter\n26. website-monitor\n27. image-reader\n28. coze-image-gen\n29. coze-voice-gen\n30. coze-web-search\n31. skill-auto-publisher\n32. youtube-title-optimizer\n\n### Recommendations\n\n1. **Use ClawHub CLI (Recommended)**:\n   ```bash\n   npm install -g clawhub\n   clawhub login\n   clawhub publish ./skill-directory --slug skill-name\n   ```\n\n2. **GitHub Auto-Import**: Configure webhook from the GitHub repo\n\n3. **Contact Support**: Request file upload API documentation\n\n### Files Generated\n- `/workspace/projects/workspace/memory/clawhub-api-report.md` - Full technical report\n- `/workspace/projects/workspace/memory/publish-attempt-2026-03-10.json` - Structured results\n- `/workspace/projects/workspace/memory/publish-results-20260310-*.json` - Raw API responses"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"kimi-k2-5-260127","usage":{"input":1601,"output":834,"cacheRead":48640,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51075,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773081188051}}
